doc.after: Nineteen customers have ordered the A380. One VIP order was made in 2007,[267] but later cancelled by Airbus.[268] Total orders for the A380 stand at 317 as of January 2015[update],[2] The biggest customer is Emirates, which has ordered or committed to order a total of 140 A380s as of 31 January 2015.[2][269] The A380F version totalled 27 orders before they were either cancelled (20) or converted to A380-800 (7), following the production delay and the subsequent suspension of the freighter programme.
